&lt;li&gt;Partner with leadership to help define go-to-market strategies, account targeting, and customer engagement approaches for these verticals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate with customers in a full-service capacity from onboarding through completion of work with a regular cadence via in-person meetings, phone calls, or electronic communication&lt;/li&gt;
