&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join Us? &lt;/strong&gt;Our Accounting team at RigUp is part of the overall Finance &amp;amp; Accounting group. We are a team of hard-working, curious, attentive, and collaborative professionals committed to financial accuracy, owning the responsibility of ensuring financial accuracy and completeness, revenue close, financial statement preparation, all the way to budgets, forecasts, board decks etc. We are growing the Finance and Accounting organization as our business continues to scale and grow. Are you ready to help us empower the people who get hard work done?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the overall month-end close functions for the RigUp group&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the development of monthly close reviews in collaboration with cross-functional teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise the Accounting team which includes review of close work and month-end analysis&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure timely, accurate, and complete financial statements close, and provide insights into results to stakeholders across the company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review and manage completion of journal entries, balance sheet reconciliations, and flux analysis for all related entities and accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and execute team efficiencies and improvements to the close process through automation, AI, standardization, and collaboration with supporting teams&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support internal and external audits and serve as a contact in the audit process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally with other groups and serve as their accounting partner, including FP&amp;amp;A, Sales, Product &amp;amp; Engineering&amp;nbsp; and Operational leaders&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research accounting issues for compliance with GAAP as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide leadership, guidance, and mentorship to the accounting team including setting clear goals and expectations for team members, conducting performance evaluations, and providing feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a collaborative and supportive work environment to maximize team productivity and morale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify training and development opportunities to enhance the skills and capabilities of the accounting team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
