&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a deep understanding of our business, customers, and product domain to inform features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Surface insights from discovery, delivery, and customer feedback that influence broader product vision and strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate discovery efforts that clarify problem areas and evaluate potential solution paths, staying curious about emerging technologies and tools that can sharpen how we build and what we deliver&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with stakeholders, operational teams, research, designers, and engineers to define and build product features, building trust through open and consistent communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help develop, prioritize, and manage a product backlog in a lean, agile environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce clearly-written product requirements and acceptance criteria that balance business and user needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with design and engineering through delivery, ensuring quality through thoughtful testing and release plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with program leaders on go-to-market plans, training materials, and customer communications&lt;/li&gt;
